## Session close reminder

After substantive work (multi-file edits, architecture decisions, or important debugging), if the user has not already said wrap up / 收尾 / skip / 跳过, ask whether to run `/session-close` for the two-question ritual:

1. What should I have asked you?
2. What am I missing?

Handoff files go in `.session-close/handoffs/` at the project root.
